SUMMARY:Acoustic Kiss + Tell: A Tribute to Sexy — Live at Watermelon Music
DESCRIPTION:Left of the Dial Promotions Presents:\nAcoustic Kiss + Tell: A Tribute to Sexy — Live at Watermelon Music\, March 20 \nGet ready for a sultry\, stripped down night of acoustic grooves as Yolo County’s Kiss + Tell brings their Tribute to Sexy to Watermelon Music in Davis on Friday\, March 20 at 7:00 PM. This special performance blends harmonies\, playful\, reimagined favorites with a warm\, unplugged edge—perfect for a cozy evening in the Melon Ball listening room. \nDoors: 7:00 PM\nShowtime: 7:30 PM\nTickets: $20 advance grants early entrance + preferred seating / Suggested $20 at the door\nVenue: Watermelon Music – 1970 Lake Blvd\, Davis\, CA \nBYOB + Heavy D’s Taco Tent will be on site. All Ages – All Inclusive \nSponsored in part by Friends of Watermelon Music\, Davis Live Music Collective\, Armadillo Music\, That California Sound! + KDRT
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/acoustic-kiss-tell-a-tribute-to-sexy-live-at-watermelon-music/
LOCATION:Melon Ball – Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, Suite #1\, Davis\, California\, 95616\, United States
